{"type": "article", "id": 13707, "title": "猫桌 2.0", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-19T07:36:11Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 33, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607133848u6yhKD5BGTxWQOz4.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一款来自 LYCS 零壹城市建筑事务所的猫桌，他们曾经在去年推出<a href=\"http://lycs-arc.com/archives/3759\" target=\"_blank\">猫桌 1.0</a>，广受好评。今年的“进阶版”不再是一个四平八稳的桌子，而是一个有着巧妙的镂空设计的立方体，不管从哪一个角度看过去，喵星人都可以找到一个玩耍的方式。同时，小方块组合在一起，可以演变出各种形态的架子，在给猫营造一个生活空间的同时，也可以放置别的物品。<a href=\"http://lycs-arc.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看 LYCS 零壹城市建筑事务所的更多作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141407zhIisRBodJHGrxkS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68854167\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141408y0VOgKqI1DfchanG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66770833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141408DjKrRM68hcdsHyaY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.42291667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141409Iogd3f0tWhB4cn8e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141409KbvzaCk3Ll4QPMeg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261414102ObFd0CK7okzDA4r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66770833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141410dGh7vrPKgy3kD9JE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}